msgstr "Taimako"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli ya haɗa da umarni da aka saka cikin manhaja don taimakawa wajen tsara"
" da gudanar da saitawsu."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Wannan shafi yana bayar da taƙaitaccen bayani na mahimman fasaloli da "
"hanyoyin kai tsaye zuwa inda za a iya sarrafa su."

