msgstr "Kwafi suna da hanya na fayil ɗin a cikin batun."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:114
msgid "Paste the copied snippet directly into the GitHub issue comment."
msgstr "Manna guntuwar da aka kwafi kai tsaye a cikin sharhi na batun GitHub."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:115
